Cryptography the/practice/and/study/of/techniques/for/secure/communication/in/the/presence/of/third/parties
Blockchain a/decentralized,/distributed/ledger/technology/that/records/transactions/across/multiple/computers/in/a/way/that/is/secure,/transparent,/and/immutable
Cybersecurity the/practice/of/protecting/computer/systems,/networks,/and/data/from/unauthorized/access,/attacks,/damage,/or/theft
Virtualization the/process/of/creating/a/virtual/representation/of/physical/resources,/such/as/computing/devices,/storage/devices,/or/networks